Images of the projection were uploaded on the Facebook page of @myswitzerland , with a caption that read: “In the city-state Singapore, different ethnic groups live together peacefully.⁣
⁣
“The country is well organised and clean: Similar characteristics are attributed to Switzerland. We show solidarity with the people of Singapore and send a sign of hope.”⁣
⁣
Sharing the post on his Facebook page, Prime Minister @leehsienloong  thanked the Swiss town for the “beautiful show of solidarity” during the Covid-19 pandemic.⁣
